---
description: SaaS multi-tenant and RBAC enforcement rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow:
- `docs/SAAS_TENANCY_MODEL.md`
- `docs/RBAC_AUTHORIZATION.md`
- `docs/ADMIN_REBUILD_PHASE_PLAN.md`

Mandatory tenancy rules:
- Build single-tenant-now but multi-tenant-ready.
- Enforce tenant/company isolation on reads, writes, and aggregates.
- Validate role + tenant ownership on every privileged mutation.
- Respect role hierarchy including `super_admin`.
- Never allow cross-tenant data leakage.
- Include tenant context in audit/log-sensitive operations.

